sql:
SELECT SUM(daily_streams) AS total_streams
FROM streaming_metrics
WHERE song_id = 12345;

external_knowledge:
- Top songs refer to the songs with the highest total stream counts; 
- Total streams include all streams for the song across different platforms and time; 
- Unique listeners are those who have listened to a song at least once; 
- Chart performance metrics include peak rank, previous rank, and days on the chart; 
- Release date is the date the song was officially released; 
- Streaming platforms refer to different online music streaming services.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT unique_listeners
FROM streaming_metrics
WHERE song_id = 12345;

SELECT SUM(unique_listeners) AS unique_listener_count
FROM streaming_metrics
WHERE song_id = 123;

